channel.title: RS2 Cache Models
channel.description:
I got really bored, so I started messing around with rs2's cache models. I'm skimming through some to see if theres any good ones to add to my client, but theres millions of them, lol. Does anyone know any good model ID numbers? I'm sticking to Character and weaponry mainly, so if you have any player model IDz that Jagex has recently made, or do you know of any good weapon model IDz, please tell me.
Btw, my email address is- helboundz@yahoo.com just incase anyone changes their mind knows any good IDz, or can answer any questions that may arise.
